OL,5, The gap between the pay of company     
OL,6, executives and other workers is set to 
OL,7, widen this year after falling during   
OL,8, the height of the Covid pandemic,      
OL,9, research by a think tank suggests.     
OL,11,FThe High Pay Centre said cuts to       
OL,12,Fexecutive pay led to a fall in the     
OL,13,Fmedian pay gap between bosses in FTSE  
OL,14,F350 firms and employees last year.     
OL,16,FBut it said early data indicated that  
OL,17,Fthe gap will widen again in 2022.      
OL,19,FPay ratios were widest in retail and   
OL,20,Flowest in media and financial services.
